<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Obadiah on Christian Internet Resources</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/obadiah/</link><description>Recent content in Obadiah on Christian Internet Resources</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><atom:link href="https://christir.org/translations/cyv/obadiah/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Obadiah 1</title><link>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/obadiah/chapter-01/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://christir.org/translations/cyv/obadiah/chapter-01/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="obadiah-chapter-1">Obadiah Chapter 1&lt;/h2>
&lt;h3 id="conversational-yahveh-covenant">Conversational Yahveh Covenant&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" align=center style='margin-top:0in;margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:.25in;text-align:center;'>&lt;b>&lt;sup>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>1&lt;/span>&lt;/sup>&lt;/b>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>The Vision of Obadiah&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="edoms-judgment-foretold">Edom’s Judgment Foretold&lt;/h3>
&lt;h3 id="the-lord-yahveh-says-this-about-edom">The Lord Yahveh says this about Edom;&lt;/h3>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      we’ve heard the report;&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>      an ambassador has gone out to the nations to say, &lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            “To arms, attack &lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%; font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Edom&lt;i>.”&lt;/i>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;b>&lt;sup>&lt;span style='font-size:14.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>         2&lt;/span>&lt;/sup>&lt;/b>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>“I’ll make you a minor player among the nations&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p>
&lt;p class="MsoListBulletCxSpMiddle" style='margin-top:0in; margin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;'>&lt;i>&lt;span style='font-size:12.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>            and utterly despised.&lt;/span>&lt;/i>&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>